ion to the\nthermodynamic limit, and also underscores the realism of dielectric continuum\ntheory down to the nanometer scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jan 2018 19:27:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Aug 2018 09:11:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-14"}
