amples establish that they indeed match. Finally, we also\nestablish a rate of density for values of homogeneous polynomials on\nhomogeneous projective varieties.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jan 2018 14:43:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-04"}
