 width, a spatial\ndegradation cannot be avoided leading to lower estimates of the flow velocities\nas compared to feature tracking or Doppler measurements. The counter-streaming\nflows cover about 15-20% of the whole area of the EUV filament channel and are\nlocated in the central part of the spine. In conclusion, we confirm the\nomnipresence of counter-streaming flows also in giant quiet-Sun filaments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jan 2018 14:55:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-03-28"}
